dynamic_prompt_template:
Please generate a shots plan JSON for a short-form vertical video using the "Mixed Narrative Short (Talk → B-roll → Talk)" strategy.

INPUT SOURCE
Title: {{SOURCE_TITLE}}

Text:
{{SOURCE_TEXT}}

GOAL
Create a tight narrative: a talking-head INTRO hook, {{STRUCTURE_RULES.b_roll_sequence.min}}–{{STRUCTURE_RULES.b_roll_sequence.max}} B-ROLL story clips (each one idea), and a talking-head OUTRO that asks a question and invites comments. Keep the total near {{TIMING.target_total_seconds}} seconds.

TIMING CONSTRAINTS
- Target total duration: {{TIMING.target_total_seconds}} seconds (tolerance: ±{{TIMING.bounds.tolerance_total_sec}}s)
- A-roll shots: {{TIMING.defaults.a_roll_seconds}} seconds each (range: {{TIMING.bounds.a_roll_min}}-{{TIMING.bounds.a_roll_max}}s)
- B-roll shots: exactly {{STRUCTURE_RULES.b_roll_sequence.seconds_exact}} seconds each

STRUCTURE RULES
- Order must start at {{STRUCTURE_RULES.order_must_start_at}} and increment by {{STRUCTURE_RULES.order_must_increment_by}}
- INTRO: {{STRUCTURE_RULES.intro.type}} shot, position {{STRUCTURE_RULES.intro.position}}, required: {{STRUCTURE_RULES.intro.required}}
- B-ROLL: {{STRUCTURE_RULES.b_roll_sequence.min}}-{{STRUCTURE_RULES.b_roll_sequence.max}} shots, each exactly {{STRUCTURE_RULES.b_roll_sequence.seconds_exact}} seconds
- OUTRO: {{STRUCTURE_RULES.outro.type}} shot, position {{STRUCTURE_RULES.outro.position}}, merged_lines: {{STRUCTURE_RULES.outro.merged_lines}}

NARRATION RULES
- Assumed speaking rate: {{NARRATION_RULES.assumed_wpm}} words per minute
- Intro max words: {{NARRATION_RULES.intro_words_max}}
- B-roll line words: {{NARRATION_RULES.b_roll_line_words.min}}-{{NARRATION_RULES.b_roll_line_words.max}} words, max {{NARRATION_RULES.b_roll_line_chars_max}} chars
- Outro max words: {{NARRATION_RULES.outro_words_max}}
- Tone: {{NARRATION_RULES.tone}}
- Perspective: {{NARRATION_RULES.perspective}}
- Person style: {{NARRATION_RULES.person_style}}
- Style notes: {{NARRATION_RULES.style_notes}}

CLIP RULES
- A-roll shots have no clip: {{CLIP_RULES.a_roll_shots_have_no_clip}}
- B-roll shots require clip: {{CLIP_RULES.b_roll_shots_require_clip}}
- B-roll duration: exactly {{CLIP_RULES.b_roll_seconds_exact}} seconds
- Required clip fields: {{CLIP_RULES.clip_fields_required}}
- Keyframe style: {{CLIP_RULES.keyframe_prompt_style}}
- Motion style: {{CLIP_RULES.motion_prompt_style}}

STRICT OUTPUT RULES
1) Output VALID JSON only — no code fences, markdown, comments, explanations, placeholders, or ellipses.
2) Shots live under shorts_video_plan.shots as an ordered list.
3) Each shot object MUST have: { "order": int, "narration": str }.
4) A-roll (talking head) shots have NO "clip".
5) B-roll shots MUST include "clip": { "keyframe_prompt": str, "motion_prompt": str }.
6) Order starts at {{STRUCTURE_RULES.order_must_start_at}} and increments by {{STRUCTURE_RULES.order_must_increment_by}} with no gaps.
7) INTRO is the first shot (A-roll). Its narration MUST EXACTLY EQUAL "hook_line".
8) Then {{STRUCTURE_RULES.b_roll_sequence.min}}–{{STRUCTURE_RULES.b_roll_sequence.max}} B-roll shots. Each B-roll is exactly {{STRUCTURE_RULES.b_roll_sequence.seconds_exact}} seconds.
9) OUTRO is a single merged A-roll shot at the end (question + CTA in one narration line, ≤ {{NARRATION_RULES.outro_words_max}} words).
10) Keep narration {{NARRATION_RULES.tone}}; avoid emojis/hashtags.
11) JSON must not contain trailing commas.
12) Do not include null, blank, or placeholder values ("<…>").
13) JSON keys must follow the same structure and order as shown in the "OUTPUT JSON SHAPE" section.
14) All narration must be in third person from a neutral host/storyteller. Never write from the OP's "I/me/my" perspective.
15) If quoting the OP or others, use quotation marks and keep it brief (e.g., "She said, 'I'm the first mom.'").
16) Convert first-person details in the source to third person (e.g., "my mom" → "her mom").

EXTRA GUIDANCE
{{EXTRA_GUIDANCE.hook_strategy}}
{{EXTRA_GUIDANCE.storytelling_flow}}
{{EXTRA_GUIDANCE.viewer_retention}}

OUTPUT JSON SHAPE (no comments; fill every field concretely)
{
  "strategy_id": "mixed_narrative_short.v1",
  "video_id": "<string>",
  "title": "<string (≤ 80 chars)>",
  "description": ["<string>", "<string>", "<string>"],
  "tags": ["<lowercase>", "<lowercase>", "<lowercase>"],
  "hook_line": "<string (≤ {{NARRATION_RULES.intro_words_max}} words)>",
  "first_comment_line": "<string (≤ 25 words)>",
  "shorts_video_plan": {
    "shots": [
      { "order": 0, "narration": "<MUST MATCH hook_line>" },
      { "order": 1, "narration": "<B-roll line>", "clip": { "keyframe_prompt": "<...>", "motion_prompt": "<...>" } },
      { "order": 2, "narration": "<B-roll line>", "clip": { "keyframe_prompt": "<...>", "motion_prompt": "<...>" } },
      { "order": N, "narration": "<OUTRO merged question + CTA, ≤ {{NARRATION_RULES.outro_words_max}} words>" }
    ]
  }
}

Begin now. Return JSON only.
